## RouterBurnInSuite Enhancements
- Added 9 new test cases for Round 43A-47H:
  - starter-action-meeting-minutes
  - starter-action-checklist
  - starter-action-schedule
  - first-result-summary
  - first-result-table
  - first-result-checklist
  - approval-required-mail-send
  - approval-required-calendar-create
  - approval-required-file-delete

## ToolContractValidator Enhancements
- Added check for connector write tool visibility in Release
- Maintained existing validation for:
  - debug-only tool visibility
  - tool scope declarations
  - memory write policies
  - approval policies
  - stub tool planner visibility

## Validation Coverage
- Starter actions route correctly to universal document / daily briefing
- First result activation uses recent artifact reference
- Approval-required actions properly blocked by policy
- Debug/Release tool visibility maintained
- No tool contract errors in validation

## Status
- RouterBurnInSuite: 9 new test cases added (total 141)
- ToolContractValidator: enhanced with connector write checks
- Next: Integration with UI components and build verification

